The paper proposes a framework for liver vessel morphology reconstruction using a fully convolutional neural network and a graph attention network. This involves image processing, computer vision, and machine learning techniques, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and medical imaging (cs.MS).
